d:**[0m\n- Confirm metrics show expected ~40 tokens/sec generation speed[0m\n- Decide if current approach is sufficient or needs refinement[0m\n- Consider adding actual token counting from content if possible[0m\n[0m\n## Relevant files / directories[0m\n[0m\n- `/home/philippe/projects/overwhellm/internal/proxy/proxy.go` - Main proxy HTTP handling, streaming logic[0m\n- `/home/philippe/projects/overwhellm/internal/proxy/token_tracker.go` - Token tracking with real-time streaming metrics[0m\n- `/home/philippe/projects/overwhellm/cmd/overwhellm/main.go` - Proxy server startup and configuration[0m\n- `/home/philippe/projects/overwhellm/` - Project root directory[0m\n[0m\n**Key code patterns to note:**[0m\n- Uses `TokenTrackingReader` wrapper for streaming body with concurrent stats tracking[0m\n- Chunks are logged with byte count and duration[0m\n- Stats calculated after streaming completes: `TotalTokens / GenerationDuration`[0m\n- Estimated tokens from bytes: `TotalBytes / 4` (assuming ~4 chars per token)[0m\n---[0m"[36m,[0m
